                <geographicDescription>South Lanarkshire - only 17 sites were surveyed in 3 peatland &apos;cluster&apos; areas, so not complete coverage of the area. The data were collected using handheld GPS to get 12 figure grid references for the majority of records allowing them to be accurately mapped in GIS</geographicDescription>
