        <methods>
            <methodStep>
                <description>
                    <para>Data collected by experienced peatland surveyors as part of commissioned work for assessments of the peatland for restoration. All species encountered during walk over surveys were recorded.</para>
                </description>
            </methodStep>
            <qualityControl>
                <description>
                    <para>This dataset was collected as part of a one-off project, by experienced peatland surveyors. Confidence it the accuracy of the dataset is high. The dataset has been checked using the NBN record cleaner, with only one record number as erroneous. This has been corrected. No other errors were picked up.</para>
                </description>
